    "This concept will be mainly discussed in Section 4.1.",
    "Intelligent design of lubrication/friction materialsThe intelligent design method for lubrication/friction materials is of great significance for the rapid design of specific components, structures, and functional materials [145,[284][285][286][287][288][289].",
    "It often efficiently predicts the performance of target products through deep integration of simulation methods and machine learning algorithms.",
    "From the perspective of the | https://mc03.manuscriptcentral.com/friction information composition of tribological systems, the main purpose of this research direction is to study the correlation between the intrinsic information of the system and its output based on the target function of the tribological system [143,[290][291][292][293][294].",
    "By designing the composition and ratio of lubricating grease, optimal friction reduction and wear resistance can be achieved [295]."
